Class LocalPrefixDeclarations

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.vlog4j.parser.LocalPrefixDeclarations
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrefixDeclarations
    public final class LocalPrefixDeclarations
extends Object
implements PrefixDeclarations
    Implementation of PrefixDeclarations that is used when parsing data from a single source. In this case, attempts to re-declare prefixes or the base IRI will lead to errors.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch
